  "title": "CREAMARE - The Game",
  "description": "In CREAMARE: The Game, players take on the role of divers to explore 9 real underwater cultural sites in the Mediterranean Sea. They must defeat a monster from the future by solving ecological challenges and puzzles related to the history of these sites.",
  "longDescription": "<!--textBlock-->\n<!--text-->\nAs part of the CREAMARE project, we're thrilled to unveil \"Creamare: The Game,\" a one-of-a-kind serious game that brings Mediterranean underwater archaeological sites to life in stunning 3D.\nOur seas are the planet's most precious “museums,” preserving a wealth of cultural treasures like shipwrecks and submerged sites. Yet, they face grave threats from human negligence and growing maritime pollution.\nIn CREAMARE: The Game, players take on the role of divers to explore 9 real underwater cultural sites in the Mediterranean Sea. They must defeat a monster from the future by solving ecological challenges and puzzles related to the history of these sites.\nThis first-person adventure game focuses on immersive exploration and engaging puzzle-solving within an interactive narrative. Get ready for an unforgettable journey, coming soon to PCs!\nJoin us in this adventure to raise awareness about the importance of preserving our underwater cultural heritage and ocean health, all while enjoying a thrilling and educational experience.\nLet's inspire a passion for protecting these invaluable treasures!\n",
